item.description: LeetCode 300. Longest Increasing Subsequence Included in my LeetCode Topic Given an unsorted array of integers, find the length of longest increasing subsequence. Example Input: [10,9,2,5,3,7,101,18] Output: 4 Explanation: The longest increasing subsequence is [2,3,7,101], therefore the length is 4.
